				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9855290#post-4118343</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9855290/scp-2348#post-4118343</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 14 Jan 2019 02:08:54 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Drblackbox</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2785951</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's a cloud that really <em>really</em> tampers with perception<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-168690-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup> and it's effects have become an epidemic, taking on cult-like properties which it seems to have either caused or responded to. This of-course carries the implication that it is an intelligent entity that <em>wants</em> humanity to go under it's weird effects. Or it's just making people think it is.</p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-168690-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. Particularly the ability to discern anything other than SCP-2348's existence.</div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
