ource: <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/ervins_strauhmanis/9536792301">https://www.flickr.com/photos/ervins_strauhmanis/9536792301</a></p> <p>(for those wondering, yes, the choice of image is very much intentional)</p> <p>Oh, one more thing that I forgot to mention: This was a self-imposed challenge on myself to write an SCP in under 500 words. This does just so, clocking in at 495 words.</p> 
